PsorAnalytics

PsorAnalytics

  • PsorAnalytics is an R package that integrates 15 psoriasis cohorts. It provides fast and convenient methods for exploring and visualizing genes of interest. Now, let’s start your analysis!
  • 1. 安装R包
  • 2. 可视化箱形图
  • 3. ROC分析
  • 4. 所有队列ROC分析景观
  • 5. 两基因相关性分析
  • 6. 差异分析
  • 7. 富集分析

Jingyuan Ning, ningjingyuan@ibms.pumc.edu.cn

2024-12-13

PsorAnalytics is an R package that integrates 15 psoriasis cohorts. It provides fast and convenient methods for exploring and visualizing genes of interest. Now, let’s start your analysis!

To access the help documentation for each function, you can type ? followed by the function name, for example ?psor_boxplot

1. 安装R包

install.packages('/Users/drning/Desktop/PsorAnalytics/PsorAnalytics_1.0.0.tar.gz')

现在我们来加载PsorAnalytics,如果没有出现报错，那么恭喜你已经安装成功了！

2. 可视化箱形图

res=psor_boxplot(gene=c('S100A12','S100A8','S100A9'),
             levels=c('healthy', 'psoriasis'),
             color= c("#A6CEE3", "#1F78B4"),
             coh='GSE117239')
## S100A12 S100A8 S100A9 can get in  GSE117239 GSE14905 GSE30999 GSE34248 GSE41662 GSE41663 GSE50790 GSE52471 GSE53552 GSE54456 GSE63979 GSE66511 GSE74697 GSE78097

3. ROC分析

5. 两基因相关性分析

res=psor_cor(gene.A='PTTG1',
         gene.B='CLEC7A',
         coh='GSE117239',
         sample.includ= c('healthy', 'psoriasis'),
         color='red',
         method='pearson',
         pt.size=1,
         pt.alpha=0.8)
## Warning: The `<scale>` argument of `guides()` cannot be `FALSE`. Use "none" instead as

6. 差异分析

deg=psor_limma(coh = 'GSE117239',
               gene.colnumber=7,
               logFC.colnumer=1,
               p.colnumber=4,
               logFC.cutoff=1,
               p.use="adj.P.Val", # "P.Value" 
               P.cutoff=0.05,
               color=c("#A6CEE3",'grey', "#1F78B4"),
               gene.marker=c('S100A12','S100A8','S100A9')
               )
## 
##   Down Notsig     Up 
##   1160  13736   1135
## Warning: Use of `plot$Type` is discouraged.
## ℹ Use `Type` instead.

7. 富集分析

#我们简单选择上调基因进行富集分析
deg=deg[["data"]]
genes=filter(deg,Type == 'Up')$gene
enrich.res=psor_enrich(genes,
            species='human')

enrichmentNetwork(enrich.res[["GO_BP"]]@result[1:300,], 
                  colorBy = 'pvalue', colorType = 'pval',
                  repelLabels = T, 
                  pCutoff = -5, fontSize =3,drawEllipses = TRUE,
                  verbose=T)+
  scale_color_gradientn(colours = c("#B83D3D",'white','#1A5592'),
                        name = "pvalue")
